entries.title: Brian Kilmeade blasts McCarthy GOP opposers for putting 'ego' over country
entries.description: Fox News host Brian Kilmeade slammed the Republican holdouts that oppose party leader Kevin McCarthy (R-CA) for next speaker of the House for putting their "ego" over the best interests of the party and country.

entries.title: Hobbs sworn in as Arizona governor
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Arizona Gov. Katie Hobbs was sworn in on Monday in a private ceremony.

entries.title: VA secretary retires as questions about vets’ home continue
